<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828777>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 13. Cosmolaelaps pampaensis, female. 6. dorsal idiosoma; 7. peritreme; 8. ventral idiosoma; 9. spermatheca; 10. epistome; 11. hypostome; 12. chelicera; 13. leg IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828777/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828775>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. 1. Cosmolaelaps guttulatus, heteromorphic male; ventral idiosoma. 2. C. pampaensis, male, ventral idiosoma; 3. C. pampaensis, male, chelicera; 4. C. pampaensis, male, leg III; 5. C. pampaensis, male, leg IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828779>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 15. Cosmolaelaps pampaensis, male, sternogenitoventral shield showing rounded processes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

